quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  3,52,‘Oh ban geurasa le Nabi Isa Awak nyan nyata kaphe keu Allah Geukheun bak rakan teuma wateenyan Soe tem bantu lon bak jalan Allah Teuma seuot le dum kawariyyun Kamoe nyang tulong agama Allah Kamoe meuiman gata keu saksi Kamoe seurah diri keupada Allah
  3,53,Hai Tuhan kamoe kamoe meuiman Peue nyang Neupeutron beuna sileupah Lom kamoe ikot peurintah Rasul Teuma Neukabui nyang kamoe peugah Neutuleh kamoe sajan ngon saksi Nyang gaseh Rabbi ureueng meutuah
  3,54,Teuma jitaki dum le awaknyan Teuma di Tuhan taki Neubalah Nyang leupah that got bak balah taki Tan laen lagi meulengkan Allah
  3,55,Yoh masa Tuhan Neukheun bak Isa Bah Lon cok gata tawoe bak Allah Bah keunoe bak Lon Lonpeuek gata Lon peugleh gata bak kaphe jadah Lon peujeut soe-soe nyang ikot gata Leubeh mulia nibak sijadah Leubeh manyang lom di ateuh kaphe Sampoe ‘an page kiamat sudah ‘Oh lheuh nyan tawoe bandum ubak Lon Sinan Lon hukom beuna ngon salah Peue nyang barokon tapeudong dawa Uroe nyan nyata hana meuilah
  3,56,Teuma sikaphe Lon azeub that-that Donya akhirat han ek soe peuglah Hana soe tulong bandum awaknyan
  3,57,Ureueng meuiman teuma meutuah Lom pih nyang pubuet amai nyang saleh Pahla cit leubeh Neubri le Allah Nyang han Neugaseh sagai le Tuhan Ureueng nyang lalem nyang pubuet salah
  3,58,Nyan keuh dum ayat nyang kamoe baca U ateuh gata hana meuilah Ayat ngon dike nyang le hikeumah Bijaksana that sidroe Potallah
  3,59,"Miseujih Isa meunyo bak Tuhan Saban ngon Adam Neupeujeut mudah Adam bak tanoh Neupeujeut ngon \"kun\" Cit jeut le rijang ban kheundak Allah"
  3,60,Atra nyang beuna nibak Po gata Bek na chok sangka meuube seupah
  3,61,Nyang peudong dawa jilawan gata ‘Oh lheuh di gata tateupue sudah Takheun leh tajak keunoe dum gata ‘Oh Iheuh di gata tateupue sudah Takheun leh tajak keunoe dum gata Teuma tamaba dum aneuk lidah Dum aneuk kamoe ngon aneuk gata Lom ngon wanita dum bandua blah Teuma droe kamoe ngon droe dum gata Bandum tamaba tameuba hilah Talakee duʻa keu soe nyang sulet Beu Neubri laknat keu jih le Allah
  3,62,Keubit nyoe teuma haba that beuna Nyang Tuhan teuma cit sidroe Allah Tan Tuhan laen nibak Droeneuhnyan Cit sidroe Tuhan nyang teuga leupah That bijaksana hana bandingan
  3,63,Meunyo jipaleng bek sang jih ka glah Tuhan Neuteupue soe pubuet fased Nyang pubuet jeuheut sabe lam salah
  3,64,Takheun jak keunoe hai ahli kitab Meusapeue pakat saboh kalimah Kamoe ngon gata beu saban that-that Taseumah meuhat sidroe Potallah Bek na peue laen tapeucharikat Tuhan Hadharat cit sidroe Allah Bek roh tacok droe ladom keu Tuhan Tapeugah Tuhan nyang bukon Allah Meunyo jipaleng han jitem pateh Gata pih ka gleh hana le salah Takheun boh jinoe beu na tama‘lum Kamoe Iseulam jok droe bak Allah
  3,65,Hai ahli kitab pakon that tangieng Akan Ibrahim nyang Rasul Allah Taurat ngon Injil kon dudoe teuka Peue nyang tadawa tapeudong hujah Ibrahim dilee kitab nyoe dudoe Pakon hana roe tapike bagah
  3,66,Ka tameudawa nyang na tateupue Nyang tan tateupue pakon tahujah Hana tateupue bandum di gata Nyang teupue saja cit sidroe Allah
  3,67,Ibrahim nyan kon ureueng Yahudi Lom kon Nasrani ban gata peugah Gopnyan Iseulam nyang gleh that ate Kon ureueng kaphe muchrek keu Allah
  3,68,Nyang patot kheun droe awak Ibrahim Teuntee soe nyang tem ikot peurintah Nyang ikot gopnyan lom pih Nabi nyoe Ngon mukmin jinoe ureueng meutuah Allah keu wali ureueng meuiman
  3,69,Nyang laen teuma saboh thaifah Saboh thaifah bak ahli kitab Jimeung peusisat gata nak salah Tapi kon gata nyang jipeusisat Droejih dum meuhat jiba lam salah Hana jiteupue droejih nyan sisat
  3,70,Hai ahli kitab pakon buet salah 7 Pakon takaphe keu ayat Tuhan Où Padahai ka trang tateupue sudah
  3,71,Hai ahli kitab pakon beureugo Nyang hak ngon bateu talawok sudah Tasom nyang beuna gata tateupue Keubit beureugo buet teuh that salah
  3,72,Na saboh kawom di ahli kitab Geuiman ligat peue nyang jipeugah Peue nyang geupeutren bak ureueng mukmin Takheun taiman beungeh beu bagah Takheun taiman bak awai uroe ‘Oh seupot uroe teuma takeubah Takaphe teuma ‘oh akhe uroe Kadang jitem woe ubak buet salah
  3,73,Soe nyang han ikot agama gata Bek tapeucaya taiman bagah Takheun peutunyok- peutunyok Tuhan Neubri keu insan nyang raya tuah Hana roe Neubri keu ureueng laen Lagee miseu nyan keu gata sudah Atawa di jih jihujah gata Jituntut gata teuma bak Allah Takheun karonya bak jaroe Tuhan Neujok atra nyan soe nyang h‘eut Allah Leupah that luah ‘eleumee Tuhan
  3,74,Soe nyang hʻeut Tuhan rahmat Neulimpah Karonya Tuhan keubit that raya Í Han ek tahingga cit le sileupah